column3: Lali-doubtless you've already guessed-ho, but another recording device has arrived from Konogg. Here.
Far as I can tell, he's sending them at regular intervals. What could the boy be up to?
Hmph, I could ask you the same. What devious scheme are you plottin'?
Well, whatever it is, you won't succeed! This is my village, and I'm not lettin' you have your way with it!
...Huh? Why did I say that? Why did I feel so angry? F-Forget I said anything...
As you can see, Glagg's still behaving strangely.

When I tried talking to him earlier, he all but told me to bugger off. On the face of it, you'd assume he takes exception to what I did at the meeting, but this is a little <Emphasis>too</Emphasis> strange...
At any rate, this is my problem to deal with, not yours. You just focus on doing your part for the cause, eh?
You obtain a message from Konogg.

The message can be viewed in your <UIForeground>F201F4</UIForeground><UIGlow>F201F5</UIGlow>Portable Archive<UIGlow>01</UIGlow><UIForeground>01</UIForeground>, which is available under Collection in the Duty section of the main menu.
